    "by using few-shot examples) and generating and voting on multiple solutions.",
    "This leads to the key knowledge gap that this study aims to address: Is the effectiveness of current chat models, such as GPT-3.5 and GPT-4, sufficient to position them as viable alternatives to established tools in the field of Alkali-Activated Concrete (AAC) formulation?",
